						<summary>

						<p>On a pillar planted in front of the Veṅkaṭēśvarasvāmi temple in the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1151, Saṅkrānti.</p>						

						<p>Records the gift of 25 cows for burning a half perpetual lamp in the temple of Mūlasthāna Mallēśvara at Telkicheṟla by Sūralakka, daughter of Sūre-Peddiṅgāru.</p>						

